Jira Tool - userful tool to sort jira stories
=============================================

|pypi| |python 3.7| |python 3.10|

.. |PyPI| image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/sharry-jira-tool.svg?style=flat-square
    :target https://pypi.org/project/sharry-jira-tool/
